OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1773155488
OL,3,CTravelodge faces pressure over
OL,4,Csecurity breach after guest sexually
OL,5,Cassaulted
OL,7,FA group of MPs has demanded urgent
OL,8,Faction from Travelodge after a man was
OL,9,Fable to talk his way into a woman's
OL,10,Fhotel room in Maidenhead and sexually
OL,11,Fassault her while she slept.
OL,13,FThe case has sparked outcry after it
OL,14,Fwas revealed 29-year-old Kyran Smith
OL,15,Fobtained a key card to the victim's
OL,16,Froom simply by claiming to be her
OL,17,Fboyfriend and providing her name.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
