PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1773155488
OL,3,CTravelodge faces pressure over
OL,4,Csecurity breach after guest sexually
OL,5,Cassaulted
OL,7,FJess Asato, the MP for Lowestoft,
OL,8,Fexpressed fury over the hotel's
OL,9,Fhandling of the aftermath, criticising
OL,10,Freports that the victim was initially
OL,11,Foffered only a #30 refund as
OL,12,Fcompensation: "If I had been the
OL,13,Fvictim of this horrendous assault and
OL,14,Flet down by the company, I would be
OL,15,Fabsolutely furious.
OL,17,F"It is a tiny and deridable amount,
OL,18,Fand it's one of the things that I
OL,19,Fthink really needs to be looked at by
OL,20,Fthe company."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
