OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1773155488
OL,3,CTravelodge faces pressure over
OL,4,Csecurity breach after guest sexually
OL,5,Cassaulted
OL,7,FWATCH: MP Jess Asato hits out at
OL,8,FTravelodge's response, calling a
OL,9,Freported #30 compensation offer a
OL,10,F"tiny and deridable amount."
OL,12,FJess Asato also challenged the hotel
OL,13,Findustry's current safety protocols,
OL,14,Fnoting that Travelodge's reliance on
OL,15,F"industry standards" suggests those
OL,16,Fvery standards are "simply not good
OL,17,Fenough" to protect vulnerable guests.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
