PN,41606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1773155488
OL,3,CTravelodge faces pressure over
OL,4,Csecurity breach after guest sexually
OL,5,Cassaulted
OL,7,FIn a statement, Boydell said: "I am
OL,8,Fcommitting to an independent review of
OL,9,Four room security policies to learn
OL,10,Ffrom this incident and further
OL,11,Fstrengthen our procedures. Our guests
OL,12,Fdeserve to be reassured that their
OL,13,Fsafety and security is of the utmost
OL,14,Fimportance to us."
OL,16,FWATCH: MP Jess Asato says women need
OL,17,Fto know that they are safe to stay in
OL,18,Fhotel rooms on their own.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1773155488
OL,3,CTravelodge faces pressure over
OL,4,Csecurity breach after guest sexually
OL,5,Cassaulted
OL,7,FThe CEO has also apologised to the
OL,8,Fvictim and offered to meet with her to
OL,9,Fdiscuss how hotel procedures can be
OL,10,Fimproved.
OL,12,FThe case has raised questions about
OL,13,Fthe duty of care within the wider
OL,14,Fhospitality sector.
OL,16,FJess Asato said: "From the studies
OL,17,Fthat have been done, we've seen that
OL,18,Fthere are quite a number of sexual
OL,19,Fassaults in hotel settings.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
