PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1773155488
OL,3,CTravelodge faces pressure over
OL,4,Csecurity breach after guest sexually
OL,5,Cassaulted
OL,7,F"The government is rolling out new
OL,8,Flegislation which will protect
OL,9,Femployees from sexual harassment. It's
OL,10,Fequally important that hotels also
OL,11,Fprotect their customers from sexual
OL,12,Fharassment and abuse."
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/8
